<i>noun</i>: 정찰 [정찰] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>정찰 [정찰]</dt><br>
<dd>1. scout; spying on</dd><br>
<dd>정보나 상황 등을 자세히 살펴서 알아냄.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of observing something to get information or figure out a situation.</dd><br>
<dd>2. reconnaissance</dd><br>
<dd>군대에서, 작전에 필요한 정보를 얻기 위해 적의 움직임이나 지형 등을 살피는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>In the military, the act of examining the movement of one's enemy or the terrain of their area to obtain information needed for an operation.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>